        <div class="about-text">
          <p>Since 1990, Dive Connections has been Central Virginia’s one-stop shop for scuba certifications, quality equipment, and unforgettable dive travel. Our PADI-certified instructors (23 on staff!) have introduced thousands to the thrill of breathing underwater, from the Blue Ridge quarries to the warm waters of the Caribbean.</p>
          <p>Whether you’re taking your very first Open Water class or gearing up for an advanced live-aboard expedition, our mission is simple: **make every dive safe, fun, and eco-conscious.** Join our dive club, fill your tanks with fresh air or Nitrox, and connect to a passionate community that dives deep together.</p>
